title: Perhaps she’s unwell
author: VD
content_html:
We were watching the Big Bang Theory last night when I noticed something. “Hey, that’s my laptop!” Yeah, that’s right, technobitches, the Dell XPS with the glowing red lights. Big fast!

Strangely, Spacebunny did not show any signs of the extreme arousal that was obviously indicated.
